MESSAGE.value: - URL http://identifiers.org/registry/ now working (the release of Grails 2.0.0.M2 might have helped) - usage new logo - renamed 'project' by 'profile' (both forms are working, also only 'profile' is mentioned in the doc) - usage QuickGo in the examples, requested by NLN - usage of "format=rdfxml" instead of "format=rdf" (more future proof), suggested by Peter Ansell - improved documentation about the content negociation, with a table summarising the various available options - usage of BioPortal PURLs for EDAM terms (should we implement a support for handling of '_' in identifiers instead of ':'?) - improved handling of 'format' parameter: URLs like "http://identifiers.org/uniprot/P12345?resource=MIR:11111111&format=rdf" not return a warning instead of a wrong RDF + more user feedback in case something is wrong - renamed "data type" in "data collection" in all public pages
